[CLS] <s>Hi, how are you? I am dealing with a lot right now!</s><s>Hello! How can I help? What is wrong?</s><s>My job is driving me nuts! I can' t handle it anymore.</s><s>How is it driving you nuts?</s><s>The pressure has been building and building. They keep giving me more responsibility, but no more help! The pandemic has really made my job a lot harder.</s><s>I have also went through the same thing as you and I know how hard it feels, so believe in yourself. You have been given responsibility because you are competent enough to carry it out.</s><s>I want to quit the job and get away from the pressure. I' m worried about my mental health and also about the risk of COVID. I think that' s the problem! I' m TOO competent.</s><s>Don' t quit your job because it will only make life harder in the long run.</s><s>I think the company wouldn' t give me so much work if I were worse at my job. <s>Hello.</s><s>Hey! How are you?</s><s>I am hanging in there, how are you doing?</s><s>Im doing good:) How you doing hanging in there?</s><s>Well, I have been dealing with insomnia, and that is pretty much ruining my day lately.</s><s>Im sorry to hear that. Have you tried to help it or see a doctor?</s><s>Yes, I have. I tried some natural things at first, but it did not work. Then I went to the doctor, and guess what? [CLS]  we are all laughing at the matter, but you can tell our boss is looking at us different. [CLS] <s>Good afternoon.</s><s>Good afternoon. How are you.</s><s>How can I be of service to you. I am well despite the virus.</s><s>I am looking for advice to help me feel better from a horrible break up. We shared many years together and I thought forever was in our minds. But he cheated on me and I do not know just what i did wrong.</s><s>Breakup from a girlfriend? Spouse.</s><s>a boyfriend/ fiance.</s><s>Sorry about that. How long ago.</s><s>Just 2 weeks ago. He proposed to me on Thanksgiving day! [CLS] <s>Hello.</s><s>Hello.</s><s>How are you today?</s><s>Really bad. My 10 year marriage is failing. Things have not gotten better.</s><s>What happened?</s><s>That' s the thing. Nothing really happened. No cheating, drugs, or abuse. I suppose the euphoria has worn off, and she just doesn' t find me interesting anymore.</s><s>I understand how you feel. Have you guys tried spending more time with each other? Maybe going out on dates?</s><s>Maybe we haven' t done this enough in the past. We both had busy careers. I tried initiating this last year, but without success. Maybe, I was too late.</s><s>Its never too late to put spice back into the relationship.</s><s>I hope you' re right. It might take a little bit but its better to try than not to try at all.</s><s>I think your suggestions are very helpful. A vacation is currently out of the picture due to COVID. I want to try having deep conversations, but I don' t know where to start.</s><s>Start by talking about whats going on. Tell her how you think you guys should spend more time with her. [CLS] <s>Can you share the dilemma you are having?</s><s>Basically. This has happened for as long as I can remember, even back when I was a little kid. Any friend i' ve ever had has just used me for SOME gain. Whether that be boredom, money, or an emotional support pillow. I' m so sick of it. They' ll literally ignore me for months and randomly text me for money. If i respond theyll read my messages then ignore me until they need money again. Or, they' ll use me to throw alllll their problems onto me and never do the same for me. In some way shape or form - every person I become friends with uses me and throws me away when theyre done.. Sometimes I feel like it must be me. Maybe i', m annoying? This happens so often the common denominator is ME. But i' m friendly, im assertive, im out spoken, im kind. I don' t LET people walk all over me but it seems like that; s all I attract..</s><s>So you feel under valued in your relationships because people tend to take advantage of you.</s><s>Pretty much. it just happens every single time. It' s kind of discouraging and just makes me an angry person.</s><s>It sounds like this is really bothering you. It is good that you are talking about it though. Have you tried telling them how they make you feel?</s><s>Some of them. The others I never even get a chance because they just ignore my existence anytime I try and reach out to talk. I' ve just been waiting for them to pour their problems onto me or have the nerve to ask for money. Then i' ll tell them. I already know they won' t respond but atleast ill say my peace.</s><s>After you tell them how you feel do you still give them money or listen to what' s going on and try to help them.</s><s>No. Whenever I do get to say my peace, i' ll just cut contact completely. Lately i' ve been holding it in and just barely responding if at all. I' ve told one of them that i have no money and she hasn' t contacted me since. But if she tries again i' ll say something about the issue. I don' t like feeling used. Who even has the nerve to blatantly use somebody like that? It' s irritating.</s><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad>[CLS]  i' ve ever had has just used me for SOME gain. [CLS] <s>How can I help you.</s><s>hi. my friend told my ex boyfriend he was an idiot for dumping me. it made me feel uncomfortable since i was in the same room. now he is talking to me again. i think he might want me back.</s><s>What are your thoughts on the relationship?</s><s>my feelings fluctuate. i resent him that he ended it. it confuses me he still wants to be in my life. he said he wanted to be friends but then asked me out again. i think he is trying to work his way back in. i know i can' t keep it up unless he makes it clear he wants to be with me. i don' t have time for games.</s><s>That does sound hard that he is giving mixed signals.</s><s>yeah i don' t like that. neither does my friend. why she told him he is an idiot for letting me go.</s><s>Do you think he took your friend' s comments seriously?</s><s>yes cuz that' s when he wanted me to be around him more.</s><s>It sounds like your friend got him thinking.</s><s>it seemed like it did.</s><s>Do you feel his change is genuine?</s><s>to a degree. i think he has ulterior motives too..</s><s>What would he have to do to prove himself?</s><s>say he wants me back or something to that effect. i' d like him to be more direct in what he wants from me.</s><s>It sounds like it would help if he were direct with you and not sending mixed signals. Is that correct?</s><s>yes that would be nice. he tends to beat around the bush then lets me know.</s><s>Have you talked to anyone else besides your friend about your concerns? [CLS] <s>Hi Thank you for your time.</s><s>Of course, I would love to hear what is going on.</s><s>Thank you. My name is DJ and I do appreciate your time.</s><s>What would you like to discuss?</s><s>I really have a desire to write a life experience book to help others overcome past failures and struggles.</s><s>That is great! I am sure so many people would benefit from the advice and outlook.</s><s>I am 66 and believe I can help others. I lack so much motivation. Thank you. That is very affirming. Yet, I have a block. I feel unworthy to write. Who am I.</s><s>It seems like it might be overwhelming for you to begin. Maybe you can start small, like think of ideas or maybe just start writing 10 minutes a day. Everybody has a story and we can all learn from others. You don' t need to a famous but just honest with what you have learned from your life.</s><s>Yes, I have been given this encouragement from other writers. My name is DJ and I do appreciate your time.</s><s>What would you like to discuss?</s><s>I really have a desire to write a life experience book to help others overcome past failures and struggles.</s><s>That is great! I am sure so many people would benefit from the advice and outlook.</s><s>I am 66 and believe I can help others. I lack so much motivation. Thank you. That is very affirming. Yet, I have a block. I feel unworthy to write. Who am I.</s><s>It seems like it might be overwhelming for you to begin. Maybe you can start small, like think of ideas or maybe just start writing 10 minutes a day. Everybody has a story and we can all learn from others. You don' t need to a famous but just honest with what you have learned from your life.</s><s>Yes, I have been given this encouragement from other writers.
